\newlabel{tab:ablation}{{5}{26}{Propagation-mode ablation (\ablSeeds {} seeds): floor change vs.\^^Mbaseline and final Gini under each inter-indicator propagation rule. Making propagation sign-aware (sign-less $\to $ documented) is the load-bearing change; the panel review is a smaller refinement on top. The utilitarian Gini is a control and barely moves}{table.caption.17}{}}
